        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Taurocletodes tumenae sp. nov. Female. A, rostrum and proximal segments of left antennule, dorsal. B, antennule, anterior. C, antenna, outer lateral. D, antennary endopod, medial. E, mandible. F, mandibular gnathobase. G, maxillule, posterior. H, maxilliped." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4634531/files/figure.png" .

